msgctxt "56_Isawa"
msgid "*pant* *pant* *pant*"
msgstr "*jadea* *jadea* *jadea*"

msgctxt "68_Tanimura"
msgid "You're under arrest, Isawa. Now come along quietly."
msgstr "Estás arrestado, Isawa. Ahora ven en silencio."

msgctxt "80_Isawa"
msgid "Screw you! I just wanna be with Fay! That's all I ever wanted!"
msgstr "¡Que te den! ¡Solo quiero estar con Fay! ¡Es todo lo que \\r siempre he querido!"

msgctxt "92_Isawa"
msgid "Why'd you have to... fuck it all up...?"
msgstr "¿Por qué has tenido que... joderlo todo...?"

msgctxt "104_Tanimura"
msgid "Isawa... You're lost, man."
msgstr "Isawa... estás perdido, amigo."

msgctxt "116_Fay"
msgid "Tanimura-san..."
msgstr "Tanimura-san..."

msgctxt "128_Isawa"
msgid "Fay... This isn't the life I wanted for us..."
msgstr "Fay... esta no es la vida que quería para nosotros..."

msgctxt "140_Fay"
msgid "Never come near me again. Understand? You stay away from me."
msgstr "Nunca te me vuelvas a acercar. ¿De acuerdo? Aléjate de mí."

msgctxt "152_Isawa"
msgid "Fay..."
msgstr "Fay..."

msgctxt "164_Tanimura"
msgid "Isawa... Whatever kind of feeling you have towards Fay, I doubt it's actually love. If it was, she wouldn't be terrified of having you around."
msgstr "Isawa... Lo que sea que sientas por Fay, dudo que sea amor. \\r Si lo fuera, Fay no viviría aterrorizada de tenerte cerca."

msgctxt "176_Isawa"
msgid "Ggh..."
msgstr "Ggh..."

msgctxt "296_Isawa"
msgid "...Tell me what I did wrong. Tell me why some jackass cop\\r\n"\n"decided on a whim to go and rip me from the love of my life!"
msgstr "...Dime qué he hecho mal. ¡Por qué un maldito policía de la\\r\n"\n"nada decidió arrancarme del amor de mi vida!"

msgctxt "308_Isawa"
msgid "Yeah, I'm talkin' about you, you little shit stain! Your boy\\r\n"\n"band-lookin' ass ever loved a woman before!? I'm guessin' the answer's no!"
msgstr "¡Sí, hablo de ti, trozo de mierda! ¿Acaso tú, con esa cara\\r\n"\n"de cantante adolescente, has amado alguna vez a una\\r\n"\n"mujer? ¡Apuesto que no!"

msgctxt "320_Isawa"
msgid "I mean, you clearly don't give a damn about Fay. You were\\r\n"\n"pretending to be her boyfriend just to get at me, right!?"
msgstr "Está claro que no te importa Fay. ¿¡Solo pretendías ser\\r\n"\n"su novio para joderme, no!?"

msgctxt "332_Isawa"
msgid "Hahaha, what a stand-up guy you are! Messin' around with\\r\n"\n"another man's girl just to feel better about your lonely, fucked-up life!"
msgstr "¡Ja ja ja, que tipo más noble! ¡Haciendo manitas con la\\r \n"\n"novia de otro para sentirte mejor en tu patética\\r \n"\n"y solitaria existencia!"

msgctxt "344_Tanimura"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "356_Policeman"
msgid "All right, pipe down! One more word out of you, and we'll add obstruction of justice, too!"
msgstr "¡Bueno, bájate dos tonitos! ¡Una palabra más y añado \\r 'obstrucción a la justicia' en la condena!"

msgctxt "404_Fay"
msgid "Tanimura-san..."
msgstr "Tanimura-san..."

msgctxt "416_Tanimura"
msgid "It's over, Fay. Isawa's more than likely headed back to prison, and I'll have some officers patrol the area for the time being."
msgstr "Se acabó, Fay. Casi seguro que Isawa vuelve a la cárcel, y \\r por ahora mandaré algunos policías que patrullen la zona."

msgctxt "428_Fay"
msgid "I don't know how to thank you... You've done so much for me. Maybe this will express... how I feel."
msgstr "No sé como agradecértelo... has hecho tanto por mí. Tal vez \\r esto demuestre... como me siento."

msgctxt "464_Tanimura"
msgid "Huh. Well, whatever it is, I'll take it."
msgstr "Eh. Bueno, sea lo que sea, lo aceptaré."

msgctxt "476_Tanimura"
msgid "Anyway, the boys'll need to get some information from you back at the station, but I'll make sure they treat you good."
msgstr "En fin, los chicos necesitarán que les informes en comisaria, \\r pero me aseguraré que te tratan bien."

msgctxt "488_Fay"
msgid "Okay... I'll trust you, Tanimura-san. Oh, and one more thing."
msgstr "De acuerdo... Confío en ti, Tanimura. Ah, y una cosa más."

msgctxt "500_Tanimura"
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr "¿Qué cosa?"

msgctxt "512_Fay"
msgid "You really are a caring, honest person. Forget what Isawa said."
msgstr "Eres una persona realmente honesta y cariñosa. No le hagas \\r caso a Isawa."

msgctxt "524_Tanimura"
msgid "Oh... Nah, that kinda stuff doesn't phase me. But I appreciate it, Fay."
msgstr "Oh... Nah, esas cosas no me afectan. Pero gracias, Fay."

msgctxt "536_Fay"
msgid "I just thought I'd let you know. Well, so long..."
msgstr "Solo te lo quería hacer saber. En fin, nos vemos..."

msgctxt "596_Tanimura"
msgid "Isawa... You don't know the first thing about me. I know who\\r\n"\n"I am and what my heart is capable of... Perhaps a little too\\r\n"\n"well."
msgstr "Isawa... No sabes nada de mí. Yo sé quién soy y de lo\\r \n"\n"que mi corazón es capaz... Puede que incluso lo sepa\\r \n"\n"demasiado bien."

